title: Legit Tits And Bent Shovels
info:
Music from the 4k intro "Legit Tits And Bent Shovels" released at Revision 2017 in the "4k PC Intro" competition.

The intro which I did together with my mate Mangosh aka "eeeevil" ended up at 10th position.

Created with Renoise using the 4Klang VST by Gopher & Powl of Alcatraz.
